53:04.139 --> 53:05.765
Let's go,
let's go!

53:08.143 --> 53:10.020
Suppressing fire!

53:10.103 --> 53:11.187
Fire!

53:12.397 --> 53:13.982
Keep 'em tight, Shames.

53:15.859 --> 53:16.860
Keep moving.

53:16.943 --> 53:18.194
Keep coming!

53:16.943 --> 53:18.194
Come on.

