Leibgott:
Krauts in the open!

53:25.410 --> 53:27.913
Keep moving!
Keep moving!

53:27.996 --> 53:29.456
Three inside!

53:31.499 --> 53:33.418
Wait a minute.
Wait a minute.
Where's Foley?

53:35.128 --> 53:36.212
Randleman!

53:37.547 --> 53:38.757
Liebgott.

53:39.883 --> 53:42.594
Where the hell
is 1st Platoon?

53:45.430 --> 53:46.640
Hold up!

53:46.723 --> 53:48.433
Keep moving!

53:48.516 --> 53:50.852
Easy Company,
hold up!

53:50.936 --> 53:52.562
2nd Platoon, hold up!

53:53.647 --> 53:55.065
Will you move!

53:55.148 --> 53:56.191
Get me Foley
on the radio.

53:56.274 --> 53:57.984
Get out of there, move!

53:58.068 --> 53:59.277
Sir, I think
we should take cover.

53:59.361 --> 54:02.280
Find some cover!
Find some cover!

54:02.364 --> 54:03.740
Find some cover!

54:03.823 --> 54:05.575
What?

54:03.823 --> 54:05.575
Stay down!

54:07.327 --> 54:09.788
Easy Red,
Easy Red, Easy Six, over.

54:09.871 --> 54:10.956
Six, Easy Red,
go ahead.

54:12.290 --> 54:15.210
Easy Red, Easy Red,
stand by for the six.

54:15.293 --> 54:18.004
Foley, Foley,
you get back here

54:18.088 --> 54:20.799
where I can
see you, godammit!

54:21.716 --> 54:23.343
1st Platoon,
hold up, hold up.

54:23.426 --> 54:25.553
Take cover!
Martin.

54:25.637 --> 54:27.597
Come on, soldier,
with me.

54:25.637 --> 54:27.597
With you, sir.

54:29.641 --> 54:30.642
Fire!

54:32.310 --> 54:34.688
Fall back!
Fall back!

54:36.064 --> 54:37.273
Take cover!

54:37.357 --> 54:38.942
Godammit.

54:39.025 --> 54:40.986
Go forward!

54:42.529 --> 54:43.530
Herron, on me.

54:43.613 --> 54:45.323
Move back.

54:43.613 --> 54:45.323
Fall back!

54:46.449 --> 54:47.534
Stay on my ass.

54:47.617 --> 54:49.244
Hold fast,
2nd Platoon.

54:49.327 --> 54:51.746
Follow Lipton!
Take cover!

54:51.830 --> 54:53.415
What are we doing,
Lieutenant?

54:53.498 --> 54:55.000
Why are we stopped?

54:55.083 --> 54:57.377
Fall back!
Fall back!

54:57.460 --> 54:59.546
Standby to six.
Roger kidnap.

54:59.629 --> 55:01.381
Foley: Lieutenant,
what's the plan?

55:01.464 --> 55:03.008
I don't know,
I don't know, I don't know!

55:04.300 --> 55:06.469
You'd better get Dike
on that radio to me now.

55:06.553 --> 55:08.096
Lieutenant,
what's the plan?

55:08.179 --> 55:10.473
Captain Winters, sir.

55:08.179 --> 55:10.473
What's the plan?

55:10.557 --> 55:11.641
Okay, okay, Foley.

55:11.725 --> 55:13.560
Foley, you take
your men--

55:13.643 --> 55:16.479
you take your men
on a flanking mission
around the village,

55:16.563 --> 55:18.440
and attack it
from the rear.

55:19.649 --> 55:22.027
Dike, we cannot
stay here!

55:22.110 --> 55:23.361
You want 1st Platoon
to go 'round

55:23.445 --> 55:25.113
and attack the village
by itself?

55:25.196 --> 55:27.032
We will provide
suppressing fire.

55:27.115 --> 55:29.325
We're gonna be kind of
alone out there, Lieutenant.

55:29.409 --> 55:32.120
We will provide
suppressing fire!

55:35.957 --> 55:37.083
Ahh!

55:39.252 --> 55:41.921
Get going forward!

55:42.005 --> 55:45.592
You need to talk
to Captain Winters, sir.

55:48.511 --> 55:51.056
Sir.

55:48.511 --> 55:51.056
Okay, here it is.

55:51.139 --> 55:53.266
We go on a flanking run
'round the back
of the village,

55:53.349 --> 55:54.768
and we attack
from the rear.

55:54.851 --> 55:56.728
Ramirez, two guys,
take 'em, go.

55:56.811 --> 55:58.354
Find some cover
behind the stable.

55:58.438 --> 55:59.647
Go, go!

56:01.107 --> 56:02.150
Shit!

56:02.233 --> 56:03.234
Jesus Christ.

56:03.318 --> 56:05.945
Webb, move up,
find cover!

56:16.539 --> 56:18.208
Suppressing fire, now!

56:20.335 --> 56:21.795
Perconte!

56:21.878 --> 56:22.962
I got you.

56:23.046 --> 56:24.756
Give me some cover!
Give me some cover!

56:27.217 --> 56:28.968
How you doing,
Perconte?

56:29.052 --> 56:31.096
They shot me
in my ass, Martin.

56:32.388 --> 56:33.973
You're all right,
stay down, stay down!

56:34.057 --> 56:35.308
I think
we lost five men.

56:35.391 --> 56:36.309
Can you locate?

56:36.392 --> 56:38.144
The building
with the caved-in roof.

56:38.228 --> 56:39.395
The building
with the caved-in roof.

56:39.479 --> 56:41.064
The building with
the caved-in roof.

56:47.570 --> 56:50.281
Sir, we are
sitting ducks here.

56:50.365 --> 56:52.283
We have to
keep moving!

56:53.201 --> 56:55.578
You've got
to keep moving!

56:55.662 --> 56:58.039
Sink:
Dick! Captain Winters.

56:58.123 --> 56:59.916
Godammit, you do not
go out there.

56:59.999 --> 57:02.669
You're
the battalion commander.
Now get back here!

57:05.046 --> 57:07.173
Now, Dick, I understand your
attachment to Easy Company--

57:07.257 --> 57:09.884
Speirs, get yourself
over here!

57:09.968 --> 57:12.887
Get out there and relieve Dike
and take that attack on in.

57:17.058 --> 57:19.435
Webb, fall back,
you're too exposed.

57:23.148 --> 57:24.941
Come on, Webb.
Let's go, kid.

57:28.027 --> 57:29.779
Hang on, Perco.

57:29.863 --> 57:30.905
Fire!

57:33.324 --> 57:35.243
Lieutenant,
what are we doing?

57:38.705 --> 57:40.874
I'm taking over.
1st Sergeant Lipton!

57:40.957 --> 57:42.584
Here!

57:40.957 --> 57:42.584
What have we got?

57:42.667 --> 57:44.669
Sir, most of the company
is spread out here.

57:44.752 --> 57:46.838
1st Platoon
tried an end around
but they're stretched out,

57:46.921 --> 57:48.298
they're pinned down
by a sniper.

57:48.381 --> 57:50.550
I believe he's in the building
with the caved-in roof.

57:50.633 --> 57:52.177
All right, I want mortars
and grenade launchers

57:52.260 --> 57:53.386
on that building
'till it's gone.

57:53.469 --> 57:54.971
When it's gone,
I want 1st to go straight in,

57:55.054 --> 57:56.556
forget going around.
Everybody else, follow me.

57:56.639 --> 57:58.558
Both: Yes, sir.

57:56.639 --> 57:58.558
Thank god, huh?

57:58.641 --> 58:00.560
All right,
3rd Platoon move out.

58:00.643 --> 58:02.395
3rd Platoon,
let's go, go, go!

58:02.478 --> 58:07.066
All right, you heard the word,
2nd Platoon, on the C.O.!

58:07.150 --> 58:08.610
Sergeant Alley!

58:07.150 --> 58:08.610
Got it, Sarge.

58:12.780 --> 58:16.701
Okay, 1st Platoon,
move out! Move out!

58:16.784 --> 58:18.453
On your feet,
2nd Platoon.

58:18.536 --> 58:19.829
Move out!

58:19.913 --> 58:21.331
Second, move out!

58:21.414 --> 58:24.667
Get on your
goddamn feet.

58:25.710 --> 58:27.378
Come on!

58:28.421 --> 58:30.673
Come on, Luz,
let's get the bastards.

58:32.759 --> 58:33.968
Fire!

58:36.262 --> 58:37.597
Come on,
move out!

58:37.680 --> 58:38.765
Man: Fire!

58:39.766 --> 58:40.725
Fire!

58:40.808 --> 58:42.518
Take cover!

58:42.602 --> 58:43.603
Fire!

58:45.521 --> 58:46.606
Go, go, go!

58:46.689 --> 58:48.024
Come on, come on.

58:50.818 --> 58:51.986
Hey, you, get over here.

58:52.070 --> 58:53.696
(men shouting)

58:55.823 --> 58:56.783
Fire!

58:56.866 --> 58:58.076
Sir.

58:56.866 --> 58:58.076
Lipton.

58:58.159 --> 59:01.162
Oh!

