Streetfight item,
streetfight item.

59:01.246 --> 59:02.914
Easy six, over.

59:02.997 --> 59:04.207
Speirs:
What do you see,
Lipton?

59:04.290 --> 59:07.001
Lipton:
Armor and infantry,
a lot of infantry.

59:07.085 --> 59:09.128
"I" Company's supposed to be
on the other side of the town.

59:09.212 --> 59:10.463
D'you see
any sign of them?

59:10.546 --> 59:12.131
Radio, anything?

59:10.546 --> 59:12.131
No, sir.

59:12.215 --> 59:13.716
Sir, I think
they're gonna pull back.

59:13.800 --> 59:15.969
If we don't connect with "I,"
they gonna slip away.

59:16.052 --> 59:17.095
That's right.
Wait here.

59:17.178 --> 59:18.888
Item, item,
easy six.

59:18.972 --> 59:20.473
What the hell?

59:22.058 --> 59:23.184
(speaking German)

59:32.193 --> 59:34.529
Lipton:
<i>At first the Germans</i>
<i>didn't shoot at him.</i>

59:34.612 --> 59:36.281
♪ ♪

59:36.364 --> 59:38.783
<i>I think they</i>
<i>couldn't quite believe</i>
<i>what they were seeing.</i>

59:38.866 --> 59:41.619
<i>But that wasn't</i>
<i>the really astounding thing.</i>

59:42.578 --> 59:43.746
<i>The astounding thing was</i>

59:43.830 --> 59:45.373
<i>that after he hooked up</i>
<i>with "I" Company...</i>

59:46.332 --> 59:47.583
<i>he came back.</i>

